data.description: NEW ROOF 2023! 3/3 POOL HOME WITH HOT TUB !! The bonus room is so spacious and can be used for a Bedrom, Office or extra Family Room for your family! This well mainatined home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living room adorned with the beautiful wood ceiling and a fire place- creating a warm and cozy ambiance. IMPACT WINDOWS AND HOT WATER HEATER (2021) NEW ELECTRICAL PANEL (2022) The highlight of this home is its dual master suites, each offering privacy and comfort both featuring en-suite bathrooms!The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the kitchen, making it ideal for entertaining guests and spending quality time with loved ones. Step outside into your own private oasis. The fenced property ensures privacy and security, making it a safe haven for children and pets to play freely. The backyard also boasts a sparkling pool, inviting you to take a refreshing dip on warm summer days or unwind by the poolside with a book in hand. Great Location! NEW ROOF October 2023!
